location.fullValue: Boxwood III Plan, Lago Mar Sales Phase 1

data.description: 5 bedroom 3 full bath home located in the gated community of Lago Mar! Oversized primary bedroom and bath downstairs, as well as a guest bedroom and a home office or study. Three bedroom upstairs with a game room and a theater room. The primary bath offers double sinks, a separate shower, and a soaking tub. The kitchen features a large island with a sink, and plenty of room to eat and entertain. Two kitchen sinks! Lots of cabinets for storage and a walk in pantry. Open concept living with a family room that flows into the kitchen and dining areas. Convenient to shopping, food, and entertainment! Lago Mar amenities include the 12 acre Lagoon plus their many events, 2 resort style pools, a splash pad, a playground, green space, a 3000 square foot resident club house, Blue Lagoon Bar & Grill, and 2 fitness centers! Lago Mar is a 100 acre resort with white sand beaches and crystal clear water! Enjoy it year round!
